            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "## i know what the issue is !\n\nwhat i am doing is using a script to clone and build Neovim for me.\ni get the source code from a URL, i.e. https://github.com/neovim/neovim.\nthe repo is then cloned in a directory whose name is `https%3A%2F%2Fgithub%2Ecom%2Fneovim%2Fneovim` (it preserves the URL but encodes it so that it does not create a bunch of sub-directories)\n\nthere are `%` format specifiers in the filenames which `luac:format` does not appear to like 😭 ",
